e of the whole particulate matter stock in oligotrophic waters (16$\,^{\circ}$S), not only in the euphotic zone (0.63 d−1) but also within the dimly lit layers of the DCM (0.36 d−1). The corresponding growth rate at 5$\,^{\circ}$S, within a quasi-mesotrophic regime, is 0.47 d−1 within the euphotic zone.},
